data.description: Unique and spacious single level ranch home on a large corner lot. A circular driveway for extra parking, and street appeal. Driftwood bleached wood walls and cathedral ceilings highlight the comfortable great room. 2 large bedrooms both with private En suite bath and walk in closets.  Corner office or den with double glass door entry, wainscoting and crown molding. Updated window package and Plantation shutters are a perfect addition. Kitchen is original country style custom design. 2 separate decks. One for relaxing and one for entertaining. Mature low maintenance landscaping. A sunroom addition overlooks a secluded back yard. Popular single level home with all the advantages of living in Lakeland Village.
